title: Part 1: Busta Rhymes Talks Losing Song to Nas & If Leaders of the New School Will Reunite
description: Brooklyn legend, Busta Rhymes stopped by Sway in the Morning to give a three part interview. Check out Busta discussing losing a record produced for him to later appear on Nas' classic Illmatic album. Along with explaining when he decided to start making solo albums, Busta revealed if the beloved, Leaders of the New School could ever reunite.
